  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you can move in sudden, swaying ways. You gain the following benefits.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Leap to Your Feet.</strong> When you're prone, you can stand up by spending 5 feet of movement, rather than half your speed.</li>\n<li><strong>Redirect Attack.</strong> When a creature misses you with a melee attack roll, you can spend 1 @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.imsZ2GYUPlwCQqqy]{ki point} as a reaction to cause that attack to hit one creature of your choice, other than the attacker, that you can see within 5 feet of you.</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: After adding this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Ki.</em></p>\n</section>",
